%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20prestigious%20corner%20of%20Wall%20Street%20is%20having%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20identity%20crisis.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20private-equity%20industry%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20some%20massive%20changes%20to%20how%20it%20recruits%20young%20talent.%20Big-name%20firms%20are%20putting%20their%20foot%20down%20about%20the%20early%20recruitment%20of%20junior%20bankers%2C%20leaving%20young%20Wall%20Streeters%20scrambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20to%20unpack%20here%2C%20so%20let's%20dive%20in%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn-cycle%20recruiting%3F%20Offers%20for%20jobs%20that%20are%20two%20years%20away%3F%20What%20is%20going%20on%20in%20private-equity%20land%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20big-name%20firms%20are%20trying%20to%20stop%20incoming%20investment-banking%20analysts%20from%20interviewing%20and%20accepting%20future-dated%20private-equity%20jobs.%20JPMorgan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-crackdown-private-equity-recruiting-junior-bankers-memo-jamie-dimon-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eformally%20warned%20incoming%20analysts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20they%20would%20be%20fired%20if%20they%20accepted%20a%20PE%20job%20offer.%20PE%20giant%20Apollo%20followed%20up%20by%20informing%20junior%20bankers%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-private-equity-recruiting-letter-2027-associates-oncycle-jpmorgan-chase-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehold%20off%20on%20recruiting%20associates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%202027%20class%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20as%20BI's%20Reed%20Alexander%20and%20Emmalyse%20Brownstein%20were%20the%20first%20to%20report%2C%20General%20Atlantic%20told%20young%20bankers%20that%20those%20job%20offers%20they%20had%20been%20prepping%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt