0rentals.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20Manny%20Reyna%20quit%20his%20project%20management%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20Tokyo%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'd%20spent%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-retired-early-in-japan-buying-rental-properties-real-estate-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20a%20portfolio%20of%20cash-flowing%20rental%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20side%20and%20was%20eager%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20his%20young%20son.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20behavior%20analyst%2C%20determined%20that%20they%20had%20enough%20coming%20in%20between%20rental%20income%20and%20her%20earnings%20to%20sustain%20their%20lifestyle%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReyna%20expects%20his%20properties%20in%20San%20Antonio%20%E2%80%94%20two%20single-family%20homes%20and%20two%20tiny%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20to%20bring%20in%20about%20%2484%2C000%20in%202025.%20He%20lists%20them%20as%20short-term%20rentals%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20Vrbo%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-increasing-cash-flow-mid-term-rentals-airbnb-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emid-term%20rentals%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Furnished%20Finder.%20He%20also%20rents%20to%20long-term%20tenants%2C%20though%20he%20prefers%20shorter%20stays%2C%20which%20require%20more%20work%20but%20are%20more%20lucrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReyna%20and%20his%20property%20manager%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Texas%2C%20co-manage%20the%20portfolio.%20Two%20software%20tools%20ensure%20that%20the%20short-term%20rental%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%20runs%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20AirDNA.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rental%20demand%20is%20a%20key%20metric%20to%20consider%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20particular.%20Are%20people%20even%20visiting%20your%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Reyna%20was%20shopping%20for%20land%20to%20place%20his%20tiny%20homes%2C%20he%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.airdna.co%2Fdata%2Fus%3Flat%3D40.43509%26lng%3D-96%26zoom%3D3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirDNA%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20answer%20that%20question.%20The%20site%20helps%20investors%20understand%20specific%20markets%20by%20providing%20data%20such%20as%20occupancy%20rates%20and%20average%20daily%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%2C%20stick%20tiny%20homes%20there%2C%20and%20then%20have%20to%20create%20some%20sort%20of%20buzz%20to%20get%20people%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20using%20AirDNA%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20different%20metrics%20like%20booking%20rates%20and%20occupancy%2C%20and%20I%20threw%20all%20the%20data%20into%20an%20Excel%20sheet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20selected%20an%20area%20with%20strong%20rental%20demand%20that%20was%20also%20within%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20of%20where%20he%20was%20living%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20has%20been%20rewarded%20with%20high%20occupancy%20rates%20for%20his%20tiny%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirDNA%20offers%20a%20free%20version%2C%20which%20provides%20limited%20market%20insights.%20The%20Pro%20version%20costs%20%2434%20a%20month%20when%20billed%20annually%20(%24400%20total%20for%20the%20year)%2C%20or%20%24125%20a%20month%20when%20billed%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20PriceLabs.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20AirDNA%20helped%20Reyna%20select%20a%20strong%20market%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhello.pricelabs.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPriceLabs%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20him%20appropriately%20price%20his%20rentals.%20The%20software%20will%20automatically%20adjust%20your%20prices%20on%20sites%20like%20Airbnb%2C%20Vrbo%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBooking.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20demand%20and%20seasonality%20in%20your%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20automates%20the%20pricing%20for%20you%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20into%20the%20apps%20and%20keep%20updating%20the%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20meant%20to%20increase%20booking%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20say%2C%20there's%20some%20special%20event%20going%20on.%20It'll%20raise%20the%20prices%20for%20you%20to%20meet%20that%20demand.%20Or%2C%20if%20nothing's%20really%20going%20on%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it'll%20lower%20the%20prices%20for%20you%20so%20that%20your%20listing%20stays%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%2030-day%20free%20trial%2C%20the%20dynamic%20pricing%20tool%20costs%20%2419.99%20per%20listing%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Reyna%2C%20the%20subscriptions%20pay%20for%20themselves%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-tools-to-help-build-grow-short-term-rental-business-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749807301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849e392f748d8c055f3849a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-tools-to-help-build-grow-short-term-rental-business-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investor%20Manny%20Reyna%20manages%20his%20properties%20remotely%2C%20with%20help%20from%20a%20property%20manager%20and%20two%20software%20tools%3A%20AirDNA%20and%20PriceLabs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A180%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-tools-to-help-build-grow-short-term-rental-business-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20swallowing%20a%20bee%20lead%20to%20Sunjay's%20death%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749807245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.c