3EIan%20Buck%20is%20a%20lesser-known%20force%20behind%20Nvidia's%20technological%20moat%20and%20market%20share.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20reputation%20as%20a%20masterful%20developer%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20Nvidia's%20history%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20Nvidia%20maintains%20its%20moat%20and%20what's%20next%20for%20the%20company%2C%20in%20part%2C%20lies%20with%20Buck.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIan%20Buck%2C%20Nvidia's%20vice%20president%20of%20hyperscale%20and%20high-performance%20computing%2C%20felt%20a%20twinge%20of%20nostalgia%20during%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang's%20keynote%20presentation%20at%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20spent%20nearly%20eight%20minutes%20on%20a%20single%20slide%20listing%20software%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20slide%20is%20genuinely%20my%20favorite%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Huang%20onstage%20in%20front%20of%2017%2C000%20people.%20%26quot%3BA%20long%20time%20ago%20%E2%80%94%2020%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20this%20slide%20was%20all%20we%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuck%20said%20he%20was%20instantly%20transported%20back%20to%202004%20when%20he%20started%20building%20the%20company's%20breakthrough%20software%2C%20called%20Compute%20Unified%20Device%20Architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20the%20team%20had%20two%20people%20and%20two%20libraries.%20Today%2C%20CUDA%20supports%20more%20than%20900%20libraries%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20models.%20Each%20library%20corresponds%20to%20an%20industry%20using%20Nvidia%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20passionate%20and%20very%20personal%20slide%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Buck%20told%20reporters%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2048-year-old's%20contribution%20to%20Nvidia%20is%20hard-coded%20into%20the%20company's%20history.%20But%20his%20influence%20is%20just%20beginning.%20CUDA%20is%20the%20platform%20from%20which%20Nvidia%20jumped%20to%2C%20at%20one%20point%2C%2090%25%20market%20share%20in%20AI%20computing.%20CUDA%20is%20how%20the%20company%20defends%20its%20moat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227637%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20all%20black%20is%20very%20small%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20shot.%20Behind%20him%20is%20a%20giant%20screen%20with%20rectangular%20shapes%20with%20illustrations%20inside%20and%20words%20below.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684ad5a385e81483682bf3a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225091%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECUDA%20started%20with%20two%20libraries.%20It%20now%20has%20more%20than%20500.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FNic%20Coury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a1f5430-90a9-41b5-a824-a8ca607a7fb8%5C%22%3EOne%20architecture%20to%20rule%20them%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDion%20Harris%2C%20Nvidia's%20senior%20director%20of%20high-performance%20computing%20and%20AI%20factory%20solutions%2C%20sometimes%20forgets%20that%20he's%20in%20the%20room%20with%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20Dr.%20Ian%20Buck.%20Then%20it%20hits%20him%20that%20his%20boss%2C%20and%20friend%2C%20is%20a%20computing%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Buck's%20undergrad%20days%20at%20Princeton%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20he%20had%20been%20focused%20on%20graphics%20%E2%80%94%20a%20particularly%20punishing%20field%20within%20computer%20science%20with%20no%20obvious%20connection%20to%20AI%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComputer%20graphics%20was%20such%20a%20dweebie%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Stephen%20Witt%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-stephen-witt-thinking-machine-book-biography-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Thinking%20Machine%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20which%20details%20Nvidia's%20rise%20from%20obscurity%20to%20the%20most%20valuable%20company%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20stigma%20to%20working%20in%20computer%20graphics%20%E2%80%94%20you%20were%20maybe%20some%20kind%20of%20man-child%20if%20this%20was%20your%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Witt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20getting%20his%20Ph.D.%20at%20Stanford%2C%20Buck%20connected%20multiple%20graphics%20processing%20units%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20stretching%20them%20to%20their%20limits.%20He%20had%20interned%20at%20Nvidia%20before%20pursuing%20his%20Ph.D.%2C%20so%20he%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20GPU.%20Initially%2C%20he%20used%20it%20for%20graphics%20like%20everyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuck%20has%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20cohort%20would%20use%20the%20chips%20to%20play%20video%20games%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BQuake%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDoom%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20eventually%2C%20he%20started%20asking%20himself%20what%20else%20his%20gaming%20setup%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20fixated%20on%20proving%20that%20you%20could%20use%20GPUs%20for%20anything%20and%20everything.%20He%20received%20funding%20from%20Nvidia%20and%20the%20Defense%20Advanced%20Research%20Projects%20Agency%2C%20among%20others%2C%20to%20develop%20tools%20to%20turn%20a%20GPU%20into%20a%20general-purpose%20supercomputing%20machine.%20When%20the%20company%20saw%20Brook%E2%80%94Buck's%20attempt%20at%20a%20programming%20language%20that%20applied%20the%20power%20of%20GPUs%20beyond%20graphics%2C%20Nvidia%20hired%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wasn't%20alone.%20John%20Nickolls%2C%20a%20hardware%20expert%20and%20then%20director%20of%20architecture%20for%20GPU%20computing%2C%20was%20also%20instrumental%20in%20building%20CUDA.%20Buck%20may%20have%20been%20forever%20paired%20with%20Nickolls%20if%20the%20latter%20had%20not%20died%20from%20cancer%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20Nickolls%20and%20Buck%20had%20this%20obsession%20with%20making%20computers%20go%20faster%20in%20the%20way%20that%20a%20Formula%201%20mechanic%20would%20have%20an%20obsession%20with%20making%20the%20race%20car%20go%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Witt%20told%20BI.%20(The%20author%20said%20Huang%20expressed%20frustration%20that%20Nickolls%20doesn't%20get%20the%20recognition%20he%20deserves%20since%20his%20passing.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuck%2C%20Nickolls%2C%20and%20a%20small%20team%20of%20experts%20built%20a%20framework%20that%20allowed%20developers%20to%20use%20an%20existing%20coding%20language%2C%20C%2C%20to%20harness%20the%20GPU's%20ability%20to%20run%20immense%20calculations%20simultaneously%20rather%20than%20one%20at%20a%20time%20and%20apply%20it%20to%20any%20field.%20The%20result%20was%20CUDA%2C%20a%20vehicle%20to%20bring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparallel%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20CUDA%20as%20an%20essential%20element%20in%20the%20world%20of%20AI%20wasn't%20inevitable.%20Huang%20insisted%20on%20making%20every%20chip%20compatible%20with%20the%20software%2C%20though%20hardly%20anyone%20was%20using%20it%20despite%20being%20free.%20In%20fact%2C%20Nvidia%20lost%20millions%20of%20dollars%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20because%20of%20CUDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20is%20lore.%20When%20ChatGPT%20launched%2C%20Nvidia%20was%20already%20powering%20the%20AI%20computing%20revolution%20that%20is%20now%20the%20focus%20of%20%247%20trillion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-massive-ai-spending-spree-quarterly-earnings-reports-calls-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einfrastructure%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20much%20of%20which%20eventually%20goes%20to%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd779c92-cc7b-429e-9b37-e20d50a8d3d3%5C%22%3EKing%20of%20the%20nerds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuck's%20smarts%20do%20have%20limits.%20He%20joked%20to%20an%20eager%20audience%20at%20GTC%20that%20quantum%20chromodynamics%2C%20a%20field%20of%20particle%20physics%2C%20just%20won't%20stick%20in%20his%20brain.%20But%20he%20thrives%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-hardcore-intensity-culture-mission-driven-jensen-huang-2025-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNvidia%2520is%2520the%2520original%2520hardcore%2CJensen%2520Huang%2527s%2520demanding%2520pace%2520reigns.%26amp%3Btext%3DNvidia%2520has%2520a%2520reputation%2520for%2Cthe%2520office%2520and%2520cut%2520perks.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20notoriously%20rigorous%3C%2Fa%3E%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Santa%20Clara%2C%20California%2C%20company%20has%20an%20intense%20culture%20that%20eschews%20one-on-one%20meetings%20and%20airs%20missteps%20and%20disagreements%20in%20public.%20It%20might%20sound%20terrifying%2C%20but%20for%20those%20with%20the%20brains%20to%20keep%20up%2C%20the%20directness%20and%20the%20rigor%20are%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20report%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20four%20people%20who%20have%20either%20worked%20directly%20with%20Buck%20at%20Stanford%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20know%20Buck%20personally%20describe%20him%20as%20gregarious%20and%20easygoing%20but%20capable%20of%20intensity%20when%20goals%20are%20on%20the%20line.%20He's%20focused%20on%20results%20rather%20than%20theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20public%20remarks%2C%20at%20panels%20and%20in%20interviews%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nvidia%2C%20Buck%20volleys%20from%20rapid%2C%20technical%20lines%20of%20thought%20to%20slower%2C%20simple%20descriptions%20in%20layman's%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20GTC%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20detailed%20the%20latest%20development%20in%20convolutional%20neural%20networks%20and%20then%20described%20proteins%20as%20%26quot%3Bcomplicated%203D%20squigglies%20in%20your%20body.%26quot%3B%20He%20describes%20the%20tiny%2C%20sensitive%20interconnects%20between%20parts%20of%20an%20Nvidia%20chipset%20like%20the%20Geek%20Squad%20explaining%20the%20back%20of%20a%20TV%20from%20memory%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20in%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20storytelling%20ability%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20the%20upper%20ranks%20at%20Nvidia.%20Since%20the%20company%20essentially%20had%20a%20promising%20technology%20waiting%20for%20a%20market%20for%20years%2C%20Huang%20still%20sees%20being%20early%20as%20a%20business%20strategy.%20He%20has%20branded%20it%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20after%20zero%20billion-dollar%20markets.%26quot%3B%20The%20potential%20of%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAI%20factories%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20spending%20that%20goes%20with%20them%20is%20a%20story%20Nvidia%20can't%20stop%20telling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuck's%20shilling%20skills%20have%20improved%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20even%20in%2015-year-old%20footage%2C%20he's%20most%20animated%20when%20explaining%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20Nvidia's%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20developers%20are%20amazing%2C%20but%20they%20say%2C%20'Leave%20me%20alone.%20I'm%20going%20to%20write%20my%20code%20in%20the%20mountains%20somewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Bloch%2C%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-partner-ddn-strategic-leap-nvidia-ai-infrastructure-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20partner%20DDN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI.%20Nvidia's%20leaders%20aren't%20like%20that%2C%20he%20said.%20Much%20of%20Nvidia's%20upper%20echelon%20may%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20match%20the%20reclusive%20set%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20choose%20between%20showmanship%20and%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286c14d7a-ca6c-47b7-be0c-a95e39f94f01%5C%22%3EIan%20Buck's%20next%20act%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIan%20Buck's%20work%20at%20Nvidia%20began%20with%20a%20simple%20mandate%3A%20make%20the%20GPU%20work%20for%20every%20industry.%20That%20mission%20is%20very%20nearly%20accomplished.%20There%20are%20hundreds%20of%20CUDA%20libraries%20targeting%20industries%20from%20weather%20forecasting%20to%20medical%20imaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20libraries%20are%20really%20there%20to%20connect%20the%20dots%20so%20that%20every%20business%20doesn't%20have%20to%20learn%20CUDA%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECUDA%20draws%20its%20strength%20from%20millions%20of%20developers%2C%20amassed%20over%20decades%2C%20who%20constantly%20innovate%20and%20improve%20on%20the%20platform.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20one%20has%20caught%20Nvidia's%20heels%2C%20but%20the%20competition%20is%20coming%20faster%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Buck%20spoke%20at%20GTC%2C%20developers%20across%20the%20world%20were%20trying%20to%20break%20through%20CUDA's%20dominance.%20The%20first%20night%20of%20the%20conference%2C%20a%20cast%20of%20competitors%20convened%20by%20TensorWave%2C%20an%20AI%20cloud%20company%20exclusively%20using%20chips%20from%20Nvidia's%20only%20US%20rival%2C%20AMD%2C%20held%20an%20event%20entitled%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20CUDA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensorwave%20cofounder%20Jeff%20Tatarchuck%20said%20it%20included%20more%20than%20%26quot%3B24%20presenters%20talking%20about%20what%20they're%20doing%20to%20overcome%20the%20CUDA%20moat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAMD%2C%20which%20also%20presented%20at%20the%20event%2C%20is%20making%20an%20explicit%20effort%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-lisa-su-ceo-nvidia-competition-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20side%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20computing%2C%20but%20industry%20analysts%20say%20they're%20not%20there%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20told%20BI%20Buck's%20team%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20speaking%20with%20researchers%20to%20stay%20on%20top.%20That's%20always%20been%20true%2C%20but%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20work%20has%20changed.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20Buck%20was%20convincing%20researchers%20to%20apply%20accelerated%20computing%20to%20their%20problems%3B%20now%20the%20tables%20have%20turned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20my%20job%20often%20is%20to%20try%20to%20predict%20the%20future%2C%20but%20AI%20is%20always%20surprising%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Buck%20said%20at%20a%20Bank%20of%20America%20conference%20this%20month.%20Understanding%20what%20the%20smartest%20minds%20in%20AI%20need%20from%20Nvidia%20is%20paramount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexplaining-deepseek-chinese-models-efficiency-scaring-markets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20that%20spooked%20markets%20with%20its%20ostensibly%20cheap%20reasoning%20AI%20model%2C%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20Nvidia%20since%20the%20team%20bypassed%20CUDA%20to%20squeeze%20out%20the%20performance%20gains%20that%20allowed%20it%20to%20achieve%20competitive%20results%20with%20less%20compute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Buck%20recently%20described%20the%20Chinese%20team%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20best%20CUDA%20developers%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20entering%20a%20new%20phase%20as%20more%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidias-success-explosive-ai-token-generation-growth-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommercialize%20their%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20with%20Nvidia's%20enormous%20head%20start%2C%20in%20part%20built%20by%20Buck%2C%20the%20pace%20is%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20one%20of%20the%20products%20Nvidia%20debuted%20at%20GTC%2C%20Dynamo%2C%20is%20an%20inference%20computing%20platform%20designed%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20reasoning%20models.%20Nvidia%20launched%20Dynamo%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20after%20the%20DeepSeek%20earthquake%2C%20but%20some%20users%20had%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-developers-stay-ahead-burn-the-boats-trash-obsolete-tech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20their%20own%20versions.%3C%2Fa%3E%20That's%20how%20fast%20AI%20is%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInference%20is%20really%20hard.%20It's%20wickedly%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Buck%20at%20GTC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalent%20is%20also%20a%20big%20part%20of%20how%20Nvidia%20is%20going%20to%20try%20to%20maintain%20its%20dominance%2C%20and%20another%20place%20where%2C%20Witt%20says%2C%20Buck%20has%20value%20beyond%20his%20technical%20skills.%20He's%20not%20exactly%20a%20household%20name%2C%20even%20at%20Stanford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20developer%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20can%20play%20in%20Buck's%20extremely%20complex%20sandbox%2C%20he%20is%20a%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20trying%20to%20hire%20these%20guys%2C%20especially%20after%20DeepSeek%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Witt.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20not%20a%20sexy%20domain%20in%20computer%20science%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Now%20it%20is%20white%20hot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20these%20guys%20are%20going%20for%20big%20money.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20Ian%20Buck%20has%20to%20be%20out%20there%20advertising%20what%20his%20group%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Witt%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20declined%20to%20make%20Ian%20Buck%20available%20for%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%20and%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280bc6866-76eb-493f-9410-3785171b33f6%5C%22%3EWho's%20Nvidia's%20next%20CEO%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuck%20is%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20younger%20than%20Huang%2C%20who%20is%2062%2C%20and%20doesn't%20plan%20on%20going%20anywhere%20anytime%20soon.%20Yet%2C%20questions%20about%20succession%20are%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsemiconductor-legend-lip-bu-tan-ai-investment-nvidia-competitors-