%20one%20of%20the%20best%20places%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20the%20best%20%E2%80%94%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20has%20even%20reignited%20one%20of%20tech's%20favorite%20fights%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-tech-week-ai-openai-thriving-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20vs.%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20month%2C%20the%20discourse%20pulsed%20through%20the%20air%20at%20New%20York%20Tech%20Week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20be%20in%20New%20York%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Julie%20Samuels%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tech%3ANYC%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20works%20with%20tech%20leaders%20in%20the%20city.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20I%20love%20about%20working%20in%20tech%20in%20New%20York%20is%20that%20people%20are%20New%20Yorkers%20first.%20To%20build%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20here%2C%20you%20really%20have%20to%20love%20New%20York.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20still%20holds%20the%20crown%20in%20venture%20funding.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20PitchBook%20and%20the%20National%20Venture%20Capital%20Association%2C%20the%20Bay%20Area%20continued%20to%20far%20outperform%20New%20York%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20with%20658%20VC%20deals%20totaling%20%2458.7%20billion%2C%20compared%20with%20441%20deals%20totaling%20%247.1%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20report%20found%20New%20York%20to%20be%20the%20city%20most%20friendly%20to%20female%20founders%2C%20with%20372%20deals%20in%20the%20first%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aedb94eb-81ae-4a96-9c9d-d8b542665519%5C%22%3EConsumer%20tech's%20comeback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20Warby%20Parker%2C%20Glossier%2C%20and%20Casper%3F%20These%20consumer%20brands%20were%20the%20face%20of%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20startups%20in%20the%202010s.%20They%20were%20design%20forward%2C%20digitally%20native%2C%20and%20ready%20to%20spar%20with%20dusty%20incumbents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20were%20also%20New%20York%20born%20and%20bred.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20success%20of%20these%20companies%20and%20others%2C%20the%20city%20became%20a%20magnet%20for%20direct-to-consumer%20startups%20across%20fashion%2C%20beauty%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20other%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20momentum%20didn't%20last%2C%20however.%20Customer%20acquisition%20costs%20soared%2C%20supply%20chains%20got%20complicated%2C%20and%20many%20of%20these%20companies%20struggled%20to%20turn%20buzz%20into%20profits.%20The%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20heightened%20the%20troubles%20facing%20many%20brands%20as%20it%20exposed%20the%20fragility%20of%20global%20logistics%20and%20hammered%20consumer%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20investors%20started%20chasing%20other%20shiny%20objects.%20The%20stalwart%20enterprise%20software%20industry%20promised%20steady%20returns.%20Crypto%20and%20Web3%20were%20capturing%20investor%20imagination.%20In%20comparison%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20VCs%20retreated%20from%20consumer%20tech.%20It%20was%20a%20tough%20sell%3A%20capital-intensive%2C%20with%20thin%20margins%20and%20operational%20headaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20seemed%20like%20another%20death%20knell%20for%20consumer%20investing.%20According%20to%20Crunchbase%20data%2C%20investments%20in%20consumer-focused%20social%20companies%20slumped%20to%20%24900%20million%20across%20just%20128%20deals%20in%202024%2C%20down%20from%20a%20%243.1%20billion%20peak%20across%20487%20deals%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%206%25%20of%20top%20VC%20firms'%20bets%20went%20to%20consumer%20startups%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20of%20PitchBook%20data%20by%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20once%20viewed%20as%20a%20setback%20for%20consumer%20startups%20is%20now%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20their%20biggest%20opportunity%2C%20investors%20and%20analysts%20say.%20AI%2C%20which%20initially%20pulled%20investor%20attention%20away%20from%20the%20space%2C%20is%20now%20powering%20a%20fresh%20wave%20of%20innovation.%20A%20new%20class%20of%20savvy%20startups%20is%20seizing%20on%20the%20technology%20to%20rethink%20how%20consumer%20businesses%20are%20built%2C%20from%20product%20development%20to%20operations%20and%20customer%20experience.%20They're%20positioning%20themselves%20to%20lead%20in%20this%20next%20chapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20consumer%20tech%20was%20previously%20defined%20by%20direct-to-consumer%20plays%20and%20mobile%20apps%2C%20this%20next%20generation%20will%20be%20shaped%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20remains%20the%20top%20investment%20theme%20for%20the%20consumer%20and%20is%20the%20largest%20opportunity%20since%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Justin%20Post%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20analyst%20note.%20%26quot%3BBusiness%20models%20around%20AI%20are%20progressing%20faster%20than%20historical%20norms%2C%20and%20are%20high%20quality%20as%20consumers%20are%20more%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4fe6a54-ae28-4c39-af1c-507bcd7cbca9%5C%22%3ENew%20York%2C%20New%20Consumer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they're%20not%20at%20a%20coffee%20meeting%20at%20La%20Cabra%20in%20SoHo%20or%20Devoci%C3%B3n%20in%20Flatiron%2C%20you%20may%20spot%20some%20of%20New%20York's%20consumer%20tech%20founders%20at%20social%20hot%20spots%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fverci-coworking-social-hub-gen-z-consumer-tech-startups-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoworking%20space%20Verci%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20out%20at%20the%20SoHo%20Equinox%20location%2C%20or%20sweating%20it%20out%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fothership-sauna-ice-baths-hotspot-nyc-tech-crowd-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOthership%20sauna%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20right%20around%