aption%5C%22%3EThe%20use%20of%20PPE%20kits%20accelerated%20the%20need%20to%20handle%20plastic%20waste%20effectively.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20humanity%20handles%20certain%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20plastics%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20fundamentally%20flawed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20turned%20something%20durable%20and%20versatile%20into%20a%20pollutant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOVID-19%20led%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20PPE%20kits%20and%20waste%20due%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20became%20very%20clear%20to%20me%3A%20we%20needed%20a%20way%20to%20give%20these%20complex%20materials%20a%20new%20life.%E2%80%9D%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20developed%20a%20breakthrough%20material%3A%20unWOOD%2C%20a%20wood-like%20substitute%20created%20from%20hard-to-recycle%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20formula%20created%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20this%20can%20be%20made%20the%20best%20use%20of.%20In%20simple%20terms%2C%20just%20like%20how%20applications%20on%20the%20phone%20show%20the%20true%20potential%20of%20smartphone%20usage%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20best%20use%20of%20unWOOD%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dr%20Babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20it%20is%20something%20called%20Macro%20Molecular%20Fibre%20Matrix%20(MMFM)%20%E2%80%94%20sounds%20technical%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20pretty%20cool.%20Imagine%20you%E2%80%99re%20cleaning%20up%20after%20a%20party%20%E2%80%94%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20mix%20of%20plastic%20wrappers%2C%20broken%20cutlery%2C%20and%20food%20containers.%20Normally%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20need%20to%20sort%20each%20type%20of%20plastic%2C%20wash%20everything%20thoroughly%2C%20and%20then%20send%20it%20off%20to%20be%20melted%20at%20high%20temperatures.%20It%E2%80%99s%20messy%2C%20energy-heavy%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20plastic%20just%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295373%2Feconiture-turns-plastic-waste-into-sustainable-furniture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eends%20up%20in%20the%20trash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22creating%20the%20material%20called%20unWOOD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T170107.402-1749641498-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447818%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Babu%20worked%20on%20changing%20the%20physical%20aspects%20of%20the%20molecule%20with%20his%20expertise.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20enter%20MMFM%20%E2%80%94%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20magic%20recipe%20created%20by%20unWOOD.%20Think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20special%20blender%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20if%20the%20plastic%20is%20clean%2C%20mixed%20up%2C%20or%20even%20hard%20to%20recycle.%20It%20combines%20all%20kinds%20of%20plastic%20with%20strong%20natural%20fibres%20and%20transforms%20them%20into%20something%20completely%20new%3A%20a%20tough%2C%20wood-like%20material%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20build%20furniture%2C%20doors%2C%20even%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20clean%20and%20melt%20plastic%20the%20old-fashioned%20way%2C%20MMFM%20takes%20the%20messy%20leftovers%20and%20turns%20them%20into%20something%20useful%2C%20without%20water%20or%20drying%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20turning%20a%20pile%20of%20junk%20into%20a%20solid%2C%20beautiful%20table%20%E2%80%94%20quickly%2C%20cleanly%2C%20and%20with%20much%20less%20environmental%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20liked%20the%20idea.%20But%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20buy%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20innovation%2C%20getting%20the%20market%20to%20adopt%20it%20was%20a%20different%20battle.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20material%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20we%20tried%20taking%20it%20to%20market%2C%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20risk.%20It%20was%20too%20new.%20Too%20unfamiliar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20unWOOD%20was%20decided%20to%20be%20offered%20only%20as%20raw%20material.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20people%20would%20buy%20the%20boards%20and%20make%20products.%20But%20most%20buyers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20try%20something%20new.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Vishal%20changed%20the%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20%E2%80%94%20let%E2%80%99s%20stop%20waiting.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20make%20the%20products%20ourselves.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20unWOOD%20became%20a%20brand%20of%20outdoor%20furniture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20how%20exactly%20does%20unWOOD%20turn%20trash%20into%20treasure%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20It%20starts%20with%20the%20waste%20no%20one%20wants%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20cities%2C%20Material%20Recovery%20Facilities%20(MRFs)%2C%20clean%20plastic%20goes%20to%20regular%20recyclers%20but%20the%20soiled%2C%20mixed%2C%20and%20multilayered%20plastic%20usually%20gets%20tossed%20aside.%20That%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20trash%20unWOOD%20picks%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22benches%20from%20unWOOD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBenches%20made%20out%20of%20unWOOD%20are%20durable%20and%20are%20perfect%20for%20outdoors.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Chopped%20and%20ready%20%E2%80%94%20the%20SAFEReCYCLER%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20stubborn%20plastic%20waste%20enters%20the%20SAFEReCYCLER%2C%20a%20powerful%20machine%20(think%3A%20an%20industrial%20blender)%20that%20grinds%20it%20all%20into%20tiny%20pieces%2C%20prepping%20it%20for%20the%20next%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20The%20magic%20mix%20%E2%80%94%20intelligent%20compounding%20engine%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20those%20plastic%20bits%20go%20into%20a%20smart%20mixer%2C%20where%20they%E2%80%99re%20combined%20with%20natural%20fibres%20using%20Dr%20Babu%E2%80%99s%20patented%20process%20without%20any%20water%2C%20high%20heat%2C%20or%20segregating%20headaches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Boards%20that%20behave%20better%20than%20wood%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20output%3F%20Strong%2C%20durable%20boards%20that%20look%20like%20wood%20but%20are%20tougher%20%E2%80%94%20resistant%20to%20moisture%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20wear.%20All%20made%20without%20harming%20a%20single%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Big%20impact%2C%20small%20footprint%3A%2044%2C000%20chips%20packets%20save%20a%20mature%20tree%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20kilo%20of%20unWOOD%20reuses%20500g%20of%20waste%20plastic%20and%20cuts%20down%20one%20and%20a%20half%20kilogram%20of%20carbon%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EunWOOD%E2%80%99s%20outdoor%20benches%2C%20tables%2C%20railings%20and%20fencing%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20niche.%20%E2%80%9CSteel%20rusts%2C%20cement%20cracks%2C%20wood%20swells%20in%20moisture%2C%20and%20plastic%20breaks%20under%20the%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20solving%20all%20of%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2011%20park%20benches%20made%20from%20unWOOD%20save%20one%20fully%20mature%20tree%2C%20and%20repurpose%20about%2014%2C000%20plastic%20bottles%2C%2044%2C000%20snack%20packets%2C%20or%201%2C500%20broken%20toys%20that%20would%20have%20otherwise%20polluted%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20officially%20launching%20as%20a%20company%20in%20April%202025%2C%20unWOOD%20has%20already%20recycled%20over%2010%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20and%20saved%2031%20trees.%20And%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20learning%20meets%20sustainability%3A%20%E2%80%98Benches%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20initiative%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20children%20in%20underserved%20Indian%20schools%20study%20seated%20on%20bare%20floors%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reality%20that%20affects%20their%20health%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20learning.%20unWOOD%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20change%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20bring%20comfort%20and%20sustainability%20into%20classrooms%20that%20had%20neither%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20our%20%E2%80%98Benches%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20initiative%20began.%E2%80%9D%20Through%20this%20programme%2C%20unWOOD%20collaborates%20with%20corporates%2C%20non-governmental%20organisations%2C%20and%20philanthropists%20to%20provide%20schools%20with%20sturdy%2C%20sustainable%20benches%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T165010.678-1749640890.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22children%20carrying%20the%20benches%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T165010.678-1749640890.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T165010.678-1749640890-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T165010.678-1749640890-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T165010.678-1749640890-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2